b_tag\" >Command Your Fleet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383150/extras/a97619aef0324f2009a8c4bc8fa3c072.poster.avif?t=1770880239\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383150/extras/a97619aef0324f2009a8c4bc8fa3c072.webm?t=1770880239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383150/extras/a97619aef0324f2009a8c4bc8fa3c072.mp4?t=1770880239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The local aliens aren't happy about your presence in the system. <strong>Command a great fleet</strong> to defend your factory and expand. Gain access to <strong>new abilities </strong>depending on your fleet composition and take on your enemies in bullet-hell style combat. Or play the game on <strong>pacifist mode</strong> for a relaxed experience!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All Music and Art is hand made, although AI was used to create voice overs and to help us indie devs write code faster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Wishlisting helps a bunch!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383150/extras/bc6481516ac7765a3700a37f596586da.poster.avif?t=1770880239\" width=616 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383150/extras/bc6481516ac7765a3700a37f596586da.webm?t=1770880239\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1383150/extras/bc6481516ac7765a3700a37f596586da.mp4?t=1770880239\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
